[SHORT DESC]
Special Attack is increased by 50% when burned.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>When the wielder is affected by burn, its Special Attack is increased by 50%.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>While <a href="/bw/pokemon/drifblim">Drifblim</a> usually prefers using one of its <a href="/bw/moves/baton_pass">Baton Pass</a> or <a href="/bw/moves/acrobatics">Acrobatics</a> sets, both of which rely on <a href="/bw/abilities/unburden">Unburden</a>, Flare Boost can give Drifblim some much needed extra firepower. A simple moveset consisting of three attacks and <a href="/bw/moves/protect">Protect</a> with a <a href="/bw/items/flame_orb">Flame Orb</a> could surprise your opponents and put a substantial dent in their defenses.</p>